/**
 * Constructs a CrAwareLexerSimulator to interpret the input
 * from the lexer.
 *
 * @param lexer
 * 		the current lexer
 * @param augmented
 * 		the augmented transition network
 * @param decisionToDfa
 * 		the DFA to store our states in
 * @param sharedContextCache
 * 		cache of PredictionContext objects
 */
public CrAwareLexerSimulator(Lexer lexer, ATN augmented, DFA[] decisionToDfa, PredictionContextCache sharedContextCache) {
    super(lexer, augmented, decisionToDfa, sharedContextCache);
}
